updateCache

public void updateCache(org.openrdf.repository.Repository rep,
                        org.openrdf.model.Resource u)
Updates the cache for the given Repository and URI. The default implementation performs a complete cache invalidation, for the repository, so it is highly recommended to re-implement this method for efficiency reason wherever possible.

size

public int size(org.openrdf.repository.Repository rep)
Return the size of the cache for the provided repository, i.e the number of KEY elements present in the cache. If rep is null, the size is returned for all repositories present in the cache.

Parameters:
rep - the repository, null is allowed
Returns:
the size of the cache (or 0 if there is no cache for the given rep)
